# CornelClean - AR Event-Logging Application

Production-ready AR application for CONEL Esports Studio promotional campaign.

## Technical Highlights
- **ARCore Integration:** Custom augmented image tracking with optimized keypoint detection
- **Database Persistence:** SQLite with thread-safe connection management
- **Android Lifecycle:** Proper async handling of camera permissions, activity transitions, session synchronization
- **External API Integration:** TTS, Scene Viewer, Discord deep-links
- **Testing Coverage:** 24 functional tests, 10 usability tests, comprehensive bug tracking

## Architecture
```
MainPage (MAUI)
├─ ARScanActivity (Native Android)
│  ├─ ARManager (ARCore session config)
│  ├─ ARSurfaceView (Hidden GL renderer)
│  └─ DetectionLogger (SQLite)
├─ ARExperiencePage (MAUI)
│  ├─ Scene Viewer (External 3D model)
│  ├─ VideoPage (Media playback)
│  └─ TTS Integration
└─ DetectionReader (SQLite query layer)
```

## Requirements
- ARCore-compatible Android device
- Internet connection (for 3D model hosting)
- Target image (included in `/docs`)

